{
  "texts": [
    "And a stirring began within Jonah's heart, a softening like unto the gentle rains that nourish the earth.",
    "In his journey, Jonah came upon a group of Ninevites who had gathered to read from the scrolls of their newfound faith.",
    "And they looked upon Jonah and beseeched him, saying, \"Man of God, will you not join us and share the wisdom of the Lord your God, for we hunger for the truth that has saved us from destruction?\"",
    "And Jonah, moved by their sincerity, sat among them and opened his mouth.",
    "He spoke of the Lord's creation, of His commandments, and of His boundless mercy."
  ]
}